      "message": "This is obviously pretty slow.  DMA obviously would help a lot here, but perhaps instead of DMAing an updated region on demand perhaps it makes more sense to maintain a shadow framebuffer and have the HW continually (~30fps) refresh via auto-restarting DMA?",
